OL,3,C'Forever our number 6' - Footballer
OL,4,Cdies after car hits multiple
OL,5,Cpedestrians
OL,7,FA 26-year-old man has died after a car
OL,8,Fmounted a kerb and struck a group of
OL,9,Fpeople, including two footballers.
OL,11,FFive pedestrians were hit by a red
OL,12,FVauxhall Astra in Arnold,
OL,13,FNottinghamshire in the early hours of
OL,14,FSaturday, 9 May. It happened in Market
OL,15,FPlace.
OL,17,FOne of the pedestrians, who can now be
OL,18,Fnamed as Tyler Fairman, was left with
OL,19,Flife-threatening injuries. He died on
OL,20,FTuesday night.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
