CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1778760670
OL,3,C'Forever our number 6' - Footballer
OL,4,Cdies after car hits multiple
OL,5,Cpedestrians
OL,7,FThe football club previously said
OL,8,Fthree members of their team, including
OL,9,Fthe manager, was hit by the car.
OL,11,FThey said their evening ended in
OL,12,F"complete heartbreak" after the crash
OL,13,Fleft one of their players "fighting
OL,14,Ffor his life".
OL,16,FDetective Chief Inspector Ruby Burrow,
OL,17,Fwho is leading the investigation for
OL,18,FNottinghamshire Police, said: "As we
OL,19,Frelease the sad news of Tyler's death,
OL,20,Four first thoughts go to his family
OL,21,Fand loved ones at this difficult time.
OL,26,@zD@_OU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
