CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1778760670
OL,3,C'Forever our number 6' - Footballer
OL,4,Cdies after car hits multiple
OL,5,Cpedestrians
OL,7,F"Both they and the other people
OL,8,Finjured or affected by this collision
OL,9,Fcontinue to be supported by specially
OL,10,Ftrained police officers.
OL,12,F"We can also confirm today that this
OL,13,Fis now a murder investigation.
OL,15,F"As such, criminal proceedings are
OL,16,Factive, so anything relating to this
OL,17,Fincident should be shared with the
OL,18,Fpolice, not online, as doing so could
OL,19,Fpotentially impede the pursuit of
OL,20,Fjustice.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
